Elasticsearch
    100% open source with no plans for commercial product
    Wikipedia is powered by elasticsearch
    Microsoft is using Elasticsearch for AD caching / Azure
    Shard size 30-50gb for optimization
    
Questions:
    Is there a good ratio of masters to minion nodes? 2 masters with max of 3
    Rolling upgrades: turn off the rebalancing / redistrbution. Then upgrade, turn it back on when done with upgrades
    
